{"tid":330001,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"大門防盜眼 外面可以睇到屋入面?","createTime":"2017-07-20T21:36:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T22:07:38.000Z","uid":42229,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a8a7f981f0a3cbdeb37bc161c8be6e5be8e01298","tid":330001,"uid":42229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T21:36:08.000Z","msg":"有次有人拍門 我用防盜眼偷睇下咩人 結果出面個人好似見到我望佢就同我揮手 示意我開門<br />\n諗諗下都幾心寒 google左一陣好似當你用眼望出去時 外面既人會見到你隻眼 真唔真?"},{"pid":"a2f6a2bc1a0998d316af0a58d53c259d721401fb","tid":330001,"uid":59930,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T21:45:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有次有人拍門 我用防盜眼偷睇下咩人 結果出面個人好似見到我望佢就同我揮手 示意我開門<br />\n諗諗下都幾心寒 google左一陣好似當你用眼望出去時 外面既人會見到你隻眼 真唔真?</blockquote><br />\n自己出去望下咪知<br />\nbtw可以見到有無光"},{"pid":"490949176c30c3b949d8d112899a702774c52036","tid":330001,"uid":49593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T21:48:21.000Z","msg":"你行埋去有影咪比人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc22e8ee0c29f941f083ea43aba8e4803997e56f","tid":330001,"uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T21:48:46.000Z","msg":"所以咪要有個蓋琴住囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89053c1bfa5a5fa6782be3ef2db7f9762e461a22","tid":330001,"uid":42229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T21:57:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以咪要有個蓋琴住囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我個隻舊式冇"},{"pid":"7071ad8e6d730d95a0a8333dede80dd26c945ebe","tid":330001,"uid":70227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T22:01:32.000Z","msg":"係可以睇返入邊"},{"pid":"ef21b8ed2f82d2148f767b7491a64a006b8ff09f","tid":330001,"uid":4677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T22:02:52.000Z","msg":"我嗰個窿塞紙巾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36015487285ca97ade954cc5b96c55ad58eb3f7b","tid":330001,"uid":4677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T22:03:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我嗰個窿塞紙巾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n嗰個防盜眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0547f76c6f0ec491ae195751439676251b71a66","tid":330001,"uid":29676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T23:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我嗰個窿塞紙巾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444ee95ce3666e15b6af3c599115011c7f28f4c1","tid":330001,"uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T21:42:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>所以咪要有個蓋琴住囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我個隻舊式冇</blockquote><br />\n用麻雀籌碼,開個窿,用電批螺絲釘釘上隻眼上面,完<br />\n我以前舊屋都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89848bfd4177c9bd70a28ceba9acb82f7d8fcf91","tid":330001,"uid":57186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T21:53:16.000Z","msg":"開心大發現?自己開門試下係外面望入屋咪知囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己就試過,係望到野既,但外面望入來係無我地望入去咁清楚既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n簡單講<br />\n外面哄隻眼望入來係望到縮到好細好唔清晰既野 (更多係類似一個透到少少光既孔咁)<br />\n入面望出去就係望到微微放大+清晰既野<br />\n<br />\n所以其實當你屋入邊有光(只要唔係夜晚+唔開燈個隻全黑),佢基本上唔洗哄埋來,只要留心睇都望到個孔既光好穩定<br />\n咁你隻眼一哄埋去望出面,外面既人咪見到個孔D光無左/黑左,佢咪知有人望,有人係裡邊囉...唔洗望到入屋都知啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9e15dbf815f0ac6252302022ce4d3f4be6f4ba","tid":330001,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T22:03:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f3daedb0c721556168c6b78e50c27ea777128f8e","tid":330001,"uid":80294,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T22:07:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開心大發現?自己開門試下係外面望入屋咪知囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己就試過,係望到野既,但外面望入來係無我地望入去咁清楚既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n簡單講<br />\n外面哄隻眼望入來係望到縮到好細好唔清晰既野 (更多係類似一個透到少少光既孔咁)<br />\n入面望出去就係望到微微放大+清晰既野<br />\n<br />\n所以其實當你屋入邊有光(只要唔係夜晚+唔開燈個隻全黑),佢基本上唔洗哄埋來,只要留心睇都望到個孔既光好穩定<br />\n咁你隻眼一哄埋去望出面,外面既人咪見到個孔D光無左/黑左,佢咪知有人望,有人係裡邊囉...唔洗望到入屋都知啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓主真係好豬兜 根本所有有過童年嘅人都一定知呢樣嘢"}]}